## DO: Contain Demo Layout

Wrap navbar+sidenav demos in fixed-height containers to prevent page-level layout shifts.

```tsx
<div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border-default" style="height: 320px">
  <ModusNavbar ... />
  <div class="flex" style="height: calc(100% - 56px)">
    <div id="content-target" class="flex-1 p-4 bg-card">
      Content area
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
```

